{"tid":1335184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你話我戇鳩都好，建制派入面我淨係撐曾鈺成一個","createTime":"2019-07-20T11:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T17:42:58.000Z","uid":52658,"like":10,"dislike":94,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ebb731ab5c2189c751bc4f1c65faa55429fe2038","tid":1335184,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"其實又唔係撐既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔反感同有少少尊敬囉<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知呢條友係老狐狸黎 老奸巨猾<br />\n大是大非前一定會歸政府邊 <br />\n佢絕對唔係同路人<br />\n但無可否認 佢做立法會主席真係比較公正中立<br />\n當時連連泛民都服佢 <br />\n睇下而家梁君彥對比下就知<br />\n成個形象出黎亦都無咁乞人憎<br />\n其實以佢地位 佢絕對唔需要企出黎扮中立<br />\n或者講埋d無稜兩可既說話<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得佢係真心為香港好<br />\n同真心愛國愛港<br />\n唔似得而家d垃圾建制派 為利益賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c28f148cad0e73206e0ad91a6a3263ad55cb82d","tid":1335184,"uid":34293,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"共產黨我淨係撐趙紫陽  其他就收皮啦屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"57acbc683f779b4c92b1097c015546b81f4ec8fc","tid":1335184,"uid":36612,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"送中直上大會，返黎就郁<br />\n你係咪失撚左憶？<br />\n屌你老母 敵人就係敵人 有咩好尊敬？"},{"pid":"9cbcd147c5a927d84b462b151bdfa57da6041097","tid":1335184,"uid":151623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"比佢沉 唔好覆/正負評"},{"pid":"3aed6dd4aa8cbe86a2d8e728b8772bf6db777636","tid":1335184,"uid":148987,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"寫十篇野讚民主派香港人<br />\n然後關鍵時刻出毒招<br />\n口蜜腹劍最陰毒<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好比佢治港<br />\n一路賣港部分香港人讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3057634056e4c0238b7752dc450c874429413a01","tid":1335184,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"57acbc683f779b4c92b1097c015546b81f4ec8fc","tid":1335184,"uid":36612,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"送中直上大會，返黎就郁<br />\n你係咪失撚左憶？<br />\n屌你老母 敵人就係敵人 有咩好尊敬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"佢一定係建制派 保皇<br />\n呢個無可否認<br />\n但佢有時同建制派唔同調 識講人話<br />\n例如佢支持唔係831框架重啟政改 同特赦年輕人<br />\n佢咁講對佢有咩好處先<br />\n只會被中央猜忌<br />\n同埋佢真係係立會主席入面最持平既一個<br />\n發言高質 飽讀詩書<br />\n我諗除左黃毓民之外無人係佢果皮"},{"pid":"77f1e98ac19d00eed28d24a0927da388d09bf15c","tid":1335184,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"教政府直上大會咪呢條友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主小同志扣一蚊"},{"pid":"c020ff34727c8bb65f6279a4928ceeac59ac195a","tid":1335184,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"81a06d5e3ae44d953704a4bb8104bb749c310687","tid":1335184,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:08:04.000Z","msg":"但大陸人嗰種衰格，佢都頂唔L住。"},{"pid":"754e4accde71de064569ce09953fe84f89ebd0df","tid":1335184,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246bb00fef564c8e537c00c80038fac8d9887e25","tid":1335184,"uid":270276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"我剩係支持毛澤東~ 以東仔既思維, 一早起香港革命~"},{"pid":"294cd1152636d95facdba43bc13125326b1bbd5c","tid":1335184,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"如果佢下屆仲出黎選既話<br />\n我當然唔會投佢<br />\n但我相信唔少淺黃絲會投票比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec382e7a21e3c4593f8af2d0e713af1aa06c1f","tid":1335184,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:13:19.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n係都田大少"},{"pid":"f7c117ed3e20a69f75e9f2afe228614d8d00600e","tid":1335184,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":4,